        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">My National Liberal colleagues in this House and those whom we represent would wish, I am certain, that we should associate ourselves in every way with the loyal expressions of sympathy to His Majesty and the Royal Family that have been made this afternoon.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
